author: cnbc.com
title: Nelnet to Announce Fourth Quarter and Year-End Results on Feb. 27
text:
LINCOLN, Neb., Jan. 9, 2018 /PRNewswire/ -- Nelnet, Inc. (NYSE: NNI) today announced it will release earnings for the fourth quarter and year ended December 31, 2017, after the close of the New York Stock Exchange on Tuesday, February 27, 2018. Upon release, additional earnings information will be available at www.nelnetinvestors.com .
Learn more about Nelnet at www.nelnet.com .
